      "title": "Lonely Colombo city",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "With the present fuel crisis, only fewer people are seen wandering around Colombo. Also the fuel and economic crisis confined people to their homes as the government has directed People to work and children to study while staying home. Due to this people are finding it tough to earn their living. Pix by Nisal Baduge"
